title: Hatyai F.C.
text: Hatyai Football Club (<a href="Thai%20alphabet">Thai</a> สโมสรฟุตบอลหาดใหญ่ ) is a Thai semi professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Hat%20Yai%20District">Hat Yai</a>, <a href="Songkhla%20Province">Songkhla Province</a>. They currently play in <a href="Thai%20League%204">Thai League 4</a> Southern Region.
